Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The distance between love and hate is filled as the two solve mysteries together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there such case?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't recycle crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that day, we set off to Akebonocho in order to arrest a serial thief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, let's catch the thief no matter wat it takes, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it feel A bit eerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have other people take over and use what can still be used
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,cherishing what limited resources we have. I'd say it's a splendid arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean recycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you don't know who the stuff was being used by previously, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need for worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there is nobody who rubs snot on everything like you do, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really do, Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You rat!\NWhat a thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,< O Tu\NStop it, don't touch 'me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's the bus headed for Akebonocho
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Victim Returns
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th 7&'s nobody in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why the thief targets this area
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you see any suspicious\Nlooking people, be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah gee, what the heck am I doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up. Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is cerebral contusion from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,being hit in the back of his head with a blunt object.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is between\N2:00 pm to 3-004 yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:04:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had nothing on him that would help us identify him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. HOsSONO...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,willyyou please explain in detail the condition in which you found the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sofa, is what I bought yesterday at sundown at a recycle shop at Beikacho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I had it delivered here at about 10:00 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, after taking a good look, the sheet was a little out of place
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I attempted to put it back in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found that lady inside the sofa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, and do you have any idea who the victim is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you yesterday between the hours of 14:00 and 15.007?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Are you suspecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's just routine procedure to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:05:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the movies yesterday afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was somebody else with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Inspector\NMegure suspects her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two things that-are~thinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sanae Hosono killed the victim and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made it look like the corpse was inside the sofa that was delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other is, a sofa with the corpse inside it is delivered just like she said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when:we over there she really looked surprised and pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't look like she was putting on an act at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the job of the police to consider all possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But .
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, the old lady's ashoes werelalso inside the sofa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why she washst wearing her shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she was killed, she was probably not wearing her shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! Which means she was killed in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she is the killer, the site of the crime is in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi go and question the neighborhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YES'; SM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, the room next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, may I ask your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1. Tokunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at your next door neighbor, Ms Hosono's room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a corpse was found in the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, Mr. Tokunaga, were, ou in your room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,between the hours of 14:001015:00 yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-work in the evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 15:00 did you hear any strange sounds or voices from next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Come to think of it,\NI sort of heard somebody arguing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard somebody arguing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what was the argument about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what was the argument about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'll be asking you about it againilater
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if what he said just now, is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's sort of hard to believe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing about her going to the movies seems to be a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to go ask around the recycle shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got curious on what the children was talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay,\NYeah, please do so then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that se>fa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an item that we bought from a customer yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean you bought it and put it out for sale right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we put the items that we purchase out for sale right 3 ay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, we can sell the item for a cheaper price
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about after\NMs. Hosono bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was here right through till closing time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was loaded on the truck for delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A oN °\NS ere any possiianity ra someone from outside can get near the truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible because the truck\NIS parked inside the warehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, of course, the warehouse is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the old lady was in there already when it was purchased...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that the previous owner of that sofa is the killer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact is, that sofa is not something that we bought from a customer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Hirose, I thought you said
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you were told to take the sofa, even if it were for free
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, yesterday afternoon, on the way back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after I went to purchase items in several places in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was around 16:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter Mr. Hirose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that, what a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It still looks very usable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You picked it up at a trash dump that youlhappened to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But manager. I felt it so wasteful to be thrown away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like that when it still\Nlooked so usable, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I lied...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I do understand your feelings of wanting to cherish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you picked it up from a trash dump
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no idea who the Killer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yea hr>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to think that the Killer carried the corpse a long wayYisnt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the trash dump that you picked that sofa up from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken. I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akebonocho 3-chome
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akebonocho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back-where we started...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, that old lady
